WEBVTT

00:06.548 --> 00:10.416
Vegeta, as much pride as you have,
you let yourself be controlled by that guy

00:10.636 --> 00:12.968
just because you wanted to get stronger?

00:13.180 --> 00:17.014
|-| wanted...

00:17.226 --> 00:22.391
I wanted... to go back to who I was before!

00:22.606 --> 00:25.814
I wanted to go back to being
the savage, cold-blooded Saiyan l was,

00:26.026 --> 00:30.235
not caring about anything
except wanting to fight you all-out!

00:31.865 --> 00:36.029
The fierce battle between Goku and Vegeta,

00:36.245 --> 00:40.454
who had returned to being
an evil warrior, went on.

00:40.666 --> 00:43.829
And as for Majin Boo's ball...

